<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Investment Basics - FinLit Portal</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/main.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/components.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ENHANCED RESPONSIVE NAVIGATION BAR -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-container">
    <!-- Logo -->
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/images/WhatsApp Image 2025-08-09 at 16.46.01_0b7ada1a.jpg" alt="FinLit Logo">
      <div>FinLit</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile Menu Toggle Button (will be created by JavaScript) -->
    <!-- Navigation Links -->
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/" >Home</a>
        <a href="/budget">Budget</a>
        <a href="/savings">Savings</a>
        <a href="/demat-simulator">Demat Simulator</a>
        <a href="/quiz">Quiz</a>
        <a href="/investments" class="active">Investments</a>
        <a href="/welcome">Login</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="hero" style="padding: 60px 20px;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>📈 Investment Basics</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Learn the fundamentals of investing and see your money grow over time!</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
  <section style="padding: 40px 0; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);">
    <div class="container">
      
      <!-- INVESTMENT BASICS CARDS -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>🎯 What is Investing?</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 30px;">
          
          <div class="concept-card" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2980b9); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;">
            <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">💡</div>
            <h3>Simple Definition</h3>
            <p>Investing means buying something today that you expect to be worth more money in the future.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="concept-card" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27ae60, #229954); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;">
            <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">🌱</div>
            <h3>Why Invest?</h3>
            <p>To grow your money over time and beat inflation, so your purchasing power increases.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="concept-card" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12, #d68910); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;">
            <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">⚖️</div>
            <h3>Risk vs Return</h3>
            <p>Higher potential returns usually come with higher risk. It's all about finding the right balance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- COMPOUND INTEREST CALCULATOR -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>🚀 Compound Interest Magic</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #666;">See how your money can grow exponentially over time!</p>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 30px;">
          
          <!-- Calculator Inputs -->
          <div class="calculator-inputs">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="initialAmount">Initial Investment (₹)</label>
              <input type="number" id="initialAmount" value="10000" min="0" max="1000000" 
                     oninput="calculateCompound()" placeholder="Enter starting amount">
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="monthlyAmount">Monthly Investment (₹)</label>
              <input type="number" id="monthlyAmount" value="1000" min="0" max="100000" 
                     oninput="calculateCompound()" placeholder="Monthly contribution">
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="interestRate">Expected Annual Return (%)</label>
              <input type="range" id="interestRate" min="1" max="20" value="12" 
                     oninput="calculateCompound(); updateRateDisplay()" style="width: 100%;">
              <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #27ae60;">
                <span id="rateDisplay">12</span>% per year
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="timePeriod">Investment Period (Years)</label>
              <input type="range" id="timePeriod" min="1" max="30" value="10" 
                     oninput="calculateCompound(); updateTimeDisplay()" style="width: 100%;">
              <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #3498db;">
                <span id="timeDisplay">10</span> years
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Results Display -->
          <div class="calculator-results">
            <div id="compoundResults">
              <!-- Results will be populated here -->
            </div>
            
            <!-- Visual Chart -->
            <div id="growthChart" style="margin-top: 20px;">
              <canvas id="chartCanvas" width="300" height="200" style="max-width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"></canvas>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- INVESTMENT TYPES -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>🏪 Types of Investments</h2>
        <div class="investment-types" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 30px;">
          
          <div class="investment-card" onclick="showInvestmentDetails('savings')" 
               style="cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.3s ease;">
            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 25px; background: white; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-left: 5px solid #27ae60;">
              <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">🏦</div>
              <h3>Savings Account</h3>
              <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                <span class="badge badge-success">Very Safe</span>
                <span class="badge badge-warning">Low Returns</span>
              </div>
              <p style="color: #666;">3-4% annual returns. Perfect for emergency funds.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="investment-card" onclick="showInvestmentDetails('fd')" 
               style="cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.3s ease;">
            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 25px; background: white; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-left: 5px solid #3498db;">
              <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">🏛️</div>
              <h3>Fixed Deposits</h3>
              <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                <span class="badge badge-success">Safe</span>
                <span class="badge badge-info">Moderate Returns</span>
              </div>
              <p style="color: #666;">5-7% annual returns. Fixed tenure with guaranteed returns.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="investment-card" onclick="showInvestmentDetails('mutual')" 
               style="cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.3s ease;">
            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 25px; background: white; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-left: 5px solid #f39c12;">
              <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">📊</div>
              <h3>Mutual Funds</h3>
              <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                <span class="badge badge-warning">Moderate Risk</span>
                <span class="badge badge-success">Good Returns</span>
              </div>
              <p style="color: #666;">10-15% potential returns. Professional fund management.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="investment-card" onclick="showInvestmentDetails('stocks')" 
               style="cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.3s ease;">
            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 25px; background: white; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-left: 5px solid #e74c3c;">
              <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">📈</div>
              <h3>Stocks</h3>
              <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                <span class="badge badge-danger">High Risk</span>
                <span class="badge badge-success">High Returns</span>
              </div>
              <p style="color: #666;">15-20%+ potential returns. Direct company ownership.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="investment-card" onclick="showInvestmentDetails('gold')" 
               style="cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.3s ease;">
            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 25px; background: white; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-left: 5px solid #f1c40f;">
              <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">🥇</div>
              <h3>Gold</h3>
              <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                <span class="badge badge-info">Moderate Risk</span>
                <span class="badge badge-warning">Inflation Hedge</span>
              </div>
              <p style="color: #666;">8-10% long-term returns. Protects against inflation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="investment-card" onclick="showInvestmentDetails('sip')" 
               style="cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.3s ease;">
            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 25px; background: white; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-left: 5px solid #9b59b6;">
              <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">🔄</div>
              <h3>SIP</h3>
              <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                <span class="badge badge-success">Disciplined</span>
                <span class="badge badge-info">Rupee Cost Averaging</span>
              </div>
              <p style="color: #666;">Systematic Investment Plan. Start with just ₹500/month!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- INVESTMENT DETAILS MODAL -->
      <div id="investmentModal" style="display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7); z-index: 1000; padding: 20px; overflow-y: auto;">
        <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 50px auto; background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 30px; position: relative;">
          <button onclick="closeInvestmentModal()" style="position: absolute; top: 15px; right: 20px; background: none; border: none; font-size: 24px; cursor: pointer;">✕</button>
          <div id="modalContent">
            <!-- Modal content will be populated here -->
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RISK TOLERANCE GAME -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>🎮 Risk vs Reward Game</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #666;">Test different investment strategies with virtual money!</p>
        
        <div class="risk-game" style="text-align: center;">
          <div class="game-stats" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <div class="stat-card">
              <div class="alert alert-success">
                <strong>💰 Portfolio Value</strong><br>
                ₹<span id="portfolioValue">1,00,000</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <div class="alert alert-info">
                <strong>📊 Total Return</strong><br>
                <span id="totalReturn">+0%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <div class="alert alert-warning">
                <strong>📈 Risk Level</strong><br>
                <span id="riskLevel">Conservative</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="investment-options" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <button onclick="makeInvestment('safe', 10000)" class="btn btn-success game-button">
              🏦 Safe Investment<br>
              <small>₹10,000 • 5-8% return • Low risk</small>
            </button>
            <button onclick="makeInvestment('moderate', 10000)" class="btn btn-warning game-button">
              📊 Moderate Investment<br>
              <small>₹10,000 • 8-15% return • Medium risk</small>
            </button>
            <button onclick="makeInvestment('risky', 10000)" class="btn btn-danger game-button">
              🚀 High Risk Investment<br>
              <small>₹10,000 • 10-25% return • High risk</small>
            </button>
          </div>
          
          <div id="gameResults" style="margin-top: 20px;"></div>
          
          <button onclick="resetGame()" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-top: 15px;">🔄 Reset Game</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SIP CALCULATOR -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>💡 SIP Calculator</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #666;">See how small monthly investments can create wealth over time!</p>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 30px;">
          <div class="sip-inputs">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="sipAmount">Monthly SIP Amount (₹)</label>
              <input type="range" id="sipAmount" min="500" max="10000" value="2000" step="500" 
                     oninput="calculateSIP(); updateSIPDisplay()" style="width: 100%;">
              <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #27ae60;">
                ₹<span id="sipAmountDisplay">2,000</span> per month
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="sipReturn">Expected Annual Return (%)</label>
              <input type="range" id="sipReturn" min="8" max="18" value="12" 
                     oninput="calculateSIP(); updateSIPReturnDisplay()" style="width: 100%;">
              <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #3498db;">
                <span id="sipReturnDisplay">12</span>% per year
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="sipPeriod">Investment Period (Years)</label>
              <input type="range" id="sipPeriod" min="1" max="25" value="15" 
                     oninput="calculateSIP(); updateSIPPeriodDisplay()" style="width: 100%;">
              <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #9b59b6;">
                <span id="sipPeriodDisplay">15</span> years
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="sip-results">
            <div id="sipResults">
              <!-- SIP results will be populated here -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- EARLY INVESTING BENEFITS -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>⏰ Power of Early Investing</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #666;">See how starting early makes a huge difference!</p>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 25px;">
          
          <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27ae60, #2ecc71); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;">
            <h3>👦 Early Bird (Age 20)</h3>
            <div style="margin: 15px 0; font-size: 1.1em;">
              <div>Monthly: ₹2,000</div>
              <div>Duration: 10 years only</div>
              <div>Total Invested: ₹2,40,000</div>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 10px; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 15px;">
              <!-- Final Value: ₹1,12,00,000 -->
               Final Value(at age 60): <br> ₹1,38,00,000
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c, #c0392b); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;">
            <h3>🏃 Late Starter (Age 30)</h3>
            <div style="margin: 15px 0; font-size: 1.1em;">
              <div>Monthly: ₹2,000</div>
              <div>Duration: 30 years</div>
              <div>Total Invested: ₹7,20,000</div>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 10px; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 15px;">
              <!-- Final Value: ₹70,60,000 -->
               Final Value(at age 60): <br> ₹70,60,000
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 15px;">
          <h3 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 15px;">🎯 Key Lesson</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #666;">The early bird invested 3 times less money but ended up with more wealth! This is the magic of compound interest over time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

